{"analytics_identifier":null,"base_path":"/government/organisations/office-for-zero-emission-vehicles/about","content_id":"a5c576dd-caa7-4847-b545-cb5bd5159bba","description":"The Office for Zero Emission Vehicles (OZEV) is a team working across government to support the transition to zero emission vehicles (ZEVs). We are providing support for the take-up of plug in vehicles, as well as funding to support chargepoint infrastructure across the UK. This will contribute to economic growth and will help reduce greenhouse gas emissions and air pollution on our roads.","details":{"attachments":[],"body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The Office for Zero Emission Vehicles (OZEV) is a team working across government to support the transition to zero emission vehicles (ZEVs). We are providing support for the take-up of plug in vehicles, as well as funding to support chargepoint infrastructure across the UK. This will contribute to economic growth and will help reduce greenhouse gas emissions and air pollution on our roads.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"responsibilities\">Responsibilities</h2>\n\n<p>We are responsible for:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>grants to reduce the upfront cost of new ultra low and zero emission vehicles</li>\n  <li>grants to install chargepoints in homes, workplaces and on residential streets</li>\n  <li>supporting charging infrastructure on the wider roads network</li>\n  <li>providing innovation support to develop zero emission vehicle technology</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2 id=\"priorities\">Priorities</h2>\n\n<p>Our priorities are to:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>ensure the UK remains one of the premier global markets for ultra low and zero emission vehicles</li>\n  <li>develop and deliver initiatives to overcome barriers to uptake of ultra low and zero emission vehicles</li>\n  <li>support innovation to put the UK at the forefront of the design, manufacture and use of zero emission vehicles</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2 id=\"who-we-are\">Who we are</h2>\n\n<p>OZEV comprises staff and funding from:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>Department for Transport</li>\n  <li>Department for Energy Security and Net Zero</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2 id=\"corporate-information\">Corporate information</h2>\n\n<h3 id=\"access-our-information\">Access our information</h3>\n\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/office-for-zero-emission-vehicles/about/research\">innovation at OZEV</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3 id=\"jobs-and-contracts\">Jobs and contracts</h3>\n\n<ul>\n  <li><a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.civilservicejobs.service.gov.uk/csr\">jobs</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Our Personal information charter explains how we treat your personal information.</p>\n\n</div>","change_history":[{"note":"First published.","public_timestamp":"2020-12-07T17:10:03Z"}],"corporate_information_groups":[{"contents":["8c94d5dd-688f-4b2f-ab28-41678abf1864"],"name":"Access our information"}],"headers":[{"id":"responsibilities","level":2,"text":"Responsibilities"},{"id":"priorities","level":2,"text":"Priorities"},{"id":"who-we-are","level":2,"text":"Who we are"},{"headers":[{"id":"access-our-information","level":3,"text":"Access our information"},{"id":"jobs-and-contracts","level":3,"text":"Jobs and contracts"}],"id":"corporate-information","level":2,"text":"Corporate information"}],"organisation":"57f7737a-90e3-4e24-9de1-b4312830b4e7","tags":{"browse_pages":[]}},"document_type":"about","first_published_at":"2020-12-07T17:10:03+00:00","links":{"available_translations":[{"api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/office-for-zero-emission-vehicles/about","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/office-for-zero-emission-vehicles/about","base_path":"/government/organisations/office-for-zero-emission-vehicles/about","content_id":"a5c576dd-caa7-4847-b545-cb5bd5159bba","document_type":"about","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2020-12-07T17:10:03Z","schema_name":"corporate_information_page","title":"About us","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/o